# cURL

Retrieve a page:
curl http://localhost

View only headers:
curl -I http://localhost

Verbose output:
curl -v http://localhost

Save a response:
curl -o response.html http://localhost

# Browser Proxy Verification

After configuring Burp:
127.0.0.1:8080
