# SQLMap (Authorized Lab Only)

Display help:
sqlmap --help

Check version:
sqlmap --version

Run detection against your local DVWA page:
sqlmap -u "http://localhost/vulnerable_page.php?id=1"

Use SQLMap only against systems you own or have explicit permission to test.
